value.name: The Voice: Generations
value.overview: The Voice Generations is a global-first special event featuring superstar coaches, coming to Channel 7 and 7plus on January 31 2022, for one week only. In a huge twist on the world’s biggest singing competition, The Voice Generations will see the nation’s greatest voices from each generation come together to perform in The Voice arena. Talented families, friends, neighbours, and even students and teachers will team up to vie for Voice glory in this special edition of the smash-hit series. Across powerful Blind Auditions and epic Battles, the generations will sing head-to-head to claim their spot in the first-ever The Voice Generations Grand Finale. And Keith Urban, Rita Ora, Guy Sebastian and Jessica Mauboy will be there to coach them along.
